    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/22f864859514ff35cfe5f113fbc0b340.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=238 height=99 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/22f864859514ff35cfe5f113fbc0b340.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Mysterious World Suspended in the Skies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Leganda, an open-world RPG where you explore floating islands once inhabited by brilliant scientists—now long gone…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One morning, you receive an <strong>enormous debt</strong> from a remote and forgotten part of the world. Searching for answers, you set off to uncover the truth.   <br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/a843f8840e6476071aa722a89d580b01.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/a843f8840e6476071aa722a89d580b01.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/a843f8840e6476071aa722a89d580b01.mp4?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon arrival, the villagers confirm that the debt is <strong>genuine yet shrouded in mystery</strong>. With no other option, you must <strong>repay it as quickly as possible</strong>. The village mayor offers you an opportunity: take over an <strong>abandoned energy production island</strong> and restore its operations. Your goal? <strong>Bring the island back to life, help revitalize the village, and unravel the secrets hidden in its past.</strong>  <br> <br>Start a New Life and Rebuild a Forgotten Island!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform an <strong>island left behind by scientists</strong> into a <strong>thriving energy hub</strong>. To succeed, you’ll need to <strong>cultivate crops, raise animals, generate electricity, and build relationships</strong> with the quirky residents of this secluded land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/07091fd1283425fc4145d517350f3c76.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=484 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/07091fd1283425fc4145d517350f3c76.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather, mine, and craft items using <strong>machines of your own design</strong>. Take part in <strong>rebuilding the village</strong> and uncover the truth behind this <strong>mysterious debt</strong> that may not be as simple as it seems. <br>  <br>                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/e7ea4703362cac5f48d4f3abb3561e23.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=400 height=401 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/e7ea4703362cac5f48d4f3abb3561e23.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be warned—this won’t be a vacation! Managing resources, upgrading equipment, and ensuring your machines have enough <strong>time and energy</strong> to operate will be <strong>a real challenge</strong>. Optimize your production, tend to your animals, and explore <strong>forgotten places filled with danger and opportunity</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Explore, trade, fight, build—there’s always something to do in Leganda!</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                            </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                              Key Features :</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Own Energy Empire</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn an abandoned island into <strong>one of the largest power production facilities</strong> in all of Leganda! Gather resources, craft machinery, and construct buildings to expand your business and maximize efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/b42f50d143807bf6eb382123ad2eb046.avif?t=1739539315\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras_big/b42f50d143807bf6eb382123ad2eb046.avif?t=1739539315 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Farm Unlike Any Other</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget traditional farming—<strong>Leganda</strong> brings a <strong>unique approach to agriculture</strong>. Grow crops in <strong>agricultural crates</strong> or use <strong>high-tech growth chambers</strong> for faster and more efficient production.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Express Your Creativity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your home <strong>however you like</strong>! Move furniture, reorganize machinery, and decorate every inch of your space. Don’t like where something is placed? <strong>Throw it overboard and start fresh!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/76183b47dfb449623bdb69d2319c7242.avif?t=1739539315\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras_big/76183b47dfb449623bdb69d2319c7242.avif?t=1739539315 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Full of Life</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surround yourself with <strong>faithful animal companions</strong>—dogs, cats, ducks, pigs, sheep, cows… even ants, birds, and flies! Every creature has its own behavior, making the world feel <strong>truly alive</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/3a7afefe485e2d76d8627d7c91b77254.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=251 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/3a7afefe485e2d76d8627d7c91b77254.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/14c715c695edffbd06467436d141ede2.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=240 height=205 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/14c715c695edffbd06467436d141ede2.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Vibrant, Dynamic Village</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet unique villagers, each with their <strong>own personality, routines, and daily lives</strong>. Some go to work, others exercise, and all have <strong>stories to share</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/0d741d43ef7362095b0beacc07ca4d93.avif?t=1739539315\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras_big/0d741d43ef7362095b0beacc07ca4d93.avif?t=1739539315 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Develop Your Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character’s growth by mastering <strong>crafting, combat, farming, or social skills</strong>. Choose the path that best fits your playstyle and unlock new opportunities.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become a Culinary Master</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find, unlock, and cook <strong>a variety of recipes</strong> using ingredients you’ve grown yourself. Each dish provides valuable bonuses to help you through tough days.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/f9de9453a7c79092a401f90de5b7c4b7.avif?t=1739539315\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras_big/f9de9453a7c79092a401f90de5b7c4b7.avif?t=1739539315 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >With your partner, <strong>venture out to capture and raise unique animals</strong>. Harvest their resources and transform them into <strong>profitable products</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Milk</strong> → Cheese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wool</strong> → Fabric</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feathers</strong> → Arrows</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meat</strong> → Gourmet dishes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/3d8b85582cc2ccd599a1a13590b46ea6.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=148 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/3d8b85582cc2ccd599a1a13590b46ea6.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/a518ec65a97f147b26364c2f337b6f58.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=213 height=193 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/a518ec65a97f147b26364c2f337b6f58.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore, Battle, and Uncover the Past</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ancient <strong>scientific laboratories and abandoned ruins</strong> hold valuable treasures—and lurking dangers. Arm yourself, venture into the unknown, and <strong>discover the secrets the Ancients left behind</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/768ad554d6f1e373f4d5949134863a89.poster.avif?t=1739539315\" width=490 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708540/extras/768ad554d6f1e373f4d5949134863a89.webm?t=1739539315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover the Hidden Truth Beneath the Village and the Power Plant…</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you’ll realize that <strong>this debt is just the beginning</strong>. The floating islands are <strong>far from stable</strong>, and something deeper is at play…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
